data.description: **Offering $10,000 Seller credit towards Buyers Rate Buy-down! 2 y/o HVAC, Energy-efficiency home nestled in the desirable Desert Oasis at Surprise Community! Split floor plan with wood-look floors in the right places, formal living & dining rooms, neutral palette, four sizable bedrooms, and two bathrooms. The ample kitchen showcases plenty of cabinets, built-in appliances, granite counters, a pantry, a breakfast bar, and a breakfast room for intimate feasts. You'll love the family room boasting sliding doors to the backyard, merging indoor/outdoor activities! Discover a split main bedroom highlighting a walk-in closet and an ensuite with dual sinks. Finally, relax in the courtyard or back-covered patio while enjoying your favorite beverage. Community amenities include a pool and parks!
